snippet.textDisplay: Hey you can sanitize a lot of makeup very easily! The things you CANT are mascara, concealer, liquid lipstick, liquid eyeliner. For eyeshadows and powders you just need to spray alcohol on top, for lipsticks and retractable liners/brow products you need to scrape the bit that's been used and spray all of it with alcohol, foundations with pumps or the ones you squeeze are good bc it doesn't get contaminated
snippet.textOriginal: Hey you can sanitize a lot of makeup very easily! The things you CANT are mascara, concealer, liquid lipstick, liquid eyeliner.
